<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link259876" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=259876&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F478476-i-m-very-confused-in-the-subtle-knife%2Fanswers%2F259876-i-wondered-this-same">flag</a>
</div>
