<div id="review_2101637647" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2101637647" />
    <a title="Snooty1" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/56024443-snooty1"><img alt="Snooty1" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1550530594p2/56024443.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2101637647?book_show_action=true">Aug 28, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Snooty1" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Snooty1" href="/user/show/56024443-snooty1">Snooty1</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56024443-snooty1?shelf=2017-books">2017-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/56024443-snooty1?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2101637647" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18288462813699571104">OH MY GOODNESS!!! This cannot be a children&apos;s book, because I am not feeling child-sized feelings right now....my heart...oh my heart....<br/>This was SOOOO good, the entire trilogy, amazing! This book, however, was the best of the entire trilogy. HANDS DOWN!<br/><br/>Wonderful, amazing, and so damn relevant. What an amazingly brave and thought provoking book....I&apos;m gushing.....This book makes me gush.<br/><br/>I can&apos;t wait for the new trilogy to come out...please find a way...(those who read it know what I&apos;m talking ab</span>
  <span id="freeText18288462813699571104" style="display:none">OH MY GOODNESS!!! This cannot be a children's book, because I am not feeling child-sized feelings right now....my heart...oh my heart....<br />This was SOOOO good, the entire trilogy, amazing! This book, however, was the best of the entire trilogy. HANDS DOWN!<br /><br />Wonderful, amazing, and so damn relevant. What an amazingly brave and thought provoking book....I'm gushing.....This book makes me gush.<br /><br />I can't wait for the new trilogy to come out...please find a way...(those who read it know what I'm talking about!)<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="18288462813699571104" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


