<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/45978.Eldest"><img alt="Eldest (The Inheritance Cycle, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1387119654l/45978._SX98_.jpg" />
